org.melior.client.rabbitmq

Class ConnectionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.client.pool.ConnectionManager<RabbitMQClientConfig,Connection,org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.connection.Connection>
      • org.melior.client.rabbitmq.ConnectionManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.connection.ConnectionFactory

    public class ConnectionManager
extends org.melior.client.pool.ConnectionManager<RabbitMQClientConfig,Connection,org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.connection.Connection>
implements org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.connection.ConnectionFactory
    Implements a manager for persistent RabbitMQ Connection objects, for connections to RabbitMQ servers. The manager writes statistics from the underlying connection pool to the logs whenever a Connection is borrowed from the pool.
    Since:
    2.3
    Author:
    Melior
